WEBVTT

00:01.167 --> 00:02.566
<i>Previously on</i> One Tree Hill.

00:02.635 --> 00:04.933
I'm not the guy for you, Brooke Davis.

00:05.005 --> 00:07.803
What if I saw someone in the car?

00:07.874 --> 00:09.273
Who?

00:09.342 --> 00:10.604
Keith.

00:10.710 --> 00:12.871
I think I still have feelings for Lucas.

00:12.946 --> 00:15.380
As far as I'm concerned,
this friendship is over.

00:15.448 --> 00:20.317
I will not have a gun-toting junkie
destroy a 17-year-old business.

00:20.387 --> 00:23.151
<i>I need the gun for protection, Karen.</i>

00:23.223 --> 00:24.986
You have Cooper's eyes.

00:25.058 --> 00:27.492
Stay the hell away from my husband.

00:28.128 --> 00:30.528
Well, you're definitely pregnant.

00:31.698 --> 00:34.428
I'm Derek. I guess I'm your brother.

00:34.534 --> 00:37.401
Ellie brought us together.
I want you to have it.

00:37.470 --> 00:39.131
Thank you, Peyton.

00:39.639 --> 00:42.836
I'm gonna find
a really special place for this.

00:46.780 --> 00:50.375
<i>There comes a time</i>
<i>when every life goes off course.</i>

00:51.418 --> 00:55.411
<i>In this desperate moment,</i>
<i>you must choose your direction.</i>

00:58.358 --> 01:00.792
<i>Will you fight to stay on the path?</i>

01:07.767 --> 01:10.565
<i>Will others tell you who you are?</i>

01:12.000 --> 01:18.074
